data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat in Humes Heights Subdivision ! This adorable 3-bedroom, 1-bath home with a bonus space upstairs offers cozy comfort and convenience. With a large yard in both the front and back, it's perfect for gatherings or gardening. Centrally located near city amenities, it's an ideal starter home or Airbnb investment. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a slice of paradise in this highly desirable neighborhood!
